<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 15:11:06 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>南非称五个国家确认加入金砖国家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-africa-says-five-countries-confirm-they-are-joining-brics-2024-01-31/</link><description>南非外交部长纳莱迪·潘多尔周三表示，埃及、埃塞俄比亚、伊朗、沙特阿拉伯和阿拉伯联合酋长国继去年受邀后已确认加入金砖国家集团。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 14:53:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-africa-says-five-countries-confirm-they-are-joining-brics-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>飞机出租人与俄罗斯就被困飞机达成和解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/aviation-lessor-settlements-with-russia-over-trapped-planes-2024-01-31/</link><description>自 2022 年莫斯科入侵乌克兰以来，俄罗斯滞留的约 400 架飞机中，有超过四分之一的飞机租赁公司已与俄罗斯达成了总额超过 25 亿美元的和解协议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 13:58:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/aviation-lessor-settlements-with-russia-over-trapped-planes-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>印度在红海附近部署前所未有的海军力量遏制海盗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india-deploys-unprecedented-naval-might-near-red-sea-rein-piracy-2024-01-31/</link><description>印度官员称，在西方列强关注伊朗支持的也门胡塞武装袭击事件之际，印度已在红海以东部署了至少十几艘军舰，以防范海盗，并调查了 250 多艘船只。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 13:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india-deploys-unprecedented-naval-might-near-red-sea-rein-piracy-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>德国经销商 Sternauto 在柏林开设比亚迪专卖店</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-dealership-sternauto-opens-byd-store-berlin-2024-01-31/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪在德国销售的五款车型将在由经销商 Sternauto 运营的柏林一家新的比亚迪专卖店展示，这是该汽车制造商正在迅速蚕食欧洲竞争对手的地盘的最新迹象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 12:38:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-dealership-sternauto-opens-byd-store-berlin-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国碧桂园计划以 5.7 亿美元出售伦敦开发项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-country-garden-looks-sell-570-million-london-development-2024-01-31/</link><description>中国房地产开发商碧桂园已将其位于伦敦东区价值4.5亿英镑（合5.7亿美元）的住宅开发项目挂牌出售，该公司在海外债务违约后正在推进国内外资产处置。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 12:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-country-garden-looks-sell-570-million-london-development-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国汽车制造商因华为计算单元出现生产问题而受到打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automakers-hit-by-production-issues-with-huawei-computing-unit-sources-2024-01-31/</link><description>五位知情人士表示，由于科技巨头华为 (HWT.UL) 制造的计算单元出现生产问题，一些中国汽车制造商不得不推迟旗舰车型的交付。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 11:32:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automakers-hit-by-production-issues-with-huawei-computing-unit-sources-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>赛默飞世尔预测 2024 年生物技术需求下滑，前景悲观</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/thermo-fisher-forecasts-2024-profit-below-estimates-biotech-demand-slump-2024-01-31/</link><description>Thermo Fisher Scientific 周三预测年度利润和收入低于华尔街预期，这表明对其用于制造治疗剂和疫苗的服务的需求将持续下滑，导致其股价下跌 2%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 11:28:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/thermo-fisher-forecasts-2024-profit-below-estimates-biotech-demand-slump-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：等待美联储决定，大型股在高位跌跌撞撞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-31/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 11:27:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>美国表示与中国的芬太尼谈判“有意义”，但还需要做更多官方工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-fentanyl-talks-with-china-meaningful-more-needs-be-done-official-2024-01-31/</link><description>白宫驻北京代表团团长周三表示，美国和中国官员之间关于阻止用于生产致命芬太尼的化学品流动的谈判是“实质性的”，但“还有更多”工作要做。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 11:04:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-fentanyl-talks-with-china-meaningful-more-needs-be-done-official-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>苹果 iPhone 销量预计温和增长，但对中国市场的担忧依然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-set-modest-iphone-sales-growth-china-worries-remain-2024-01-31/</link><description>苹果 iPhone 销量在关键假期期间可能增长 3%，这是五个季度以来的最佳增长，但分析师预计该公司在中国将面临艰难的一年，因为该公司在中国面临监管阻力和来自华为的激烈竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 11:02:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-set-modest-iphone-sales-growth-china-worries-remain-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>台军模拟中国将演习变成攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-military-simulates-china-turning-drills-into-an-attack-2024-01-31/</link><description>台湾军方周三模拟了中国突然将其一次环岛定期演习转变为实际攻击的场景，同一天中国在台湾附近进行了另一次“战备巡逻”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:37:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-military-simulates-china-turning-drills-into-an-attack-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>FBI局长出庭作证，中国黑客瞄准美国基础设施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-are-targeting-us-infrastructure-fbi-chief-testify-2024-01-31/</link><description>联邦调查局局长计划周三告诉一个小组，中国黑客正在瞄准美国的关键基础设施，准备对美国人造成“现实世界的伤害”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:15:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-are-targeting-us-infrastructure-fbi-chief-testify-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>战争后勤：华盛顿如何为中国入侵台湾做准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/logistics-war-how-washington-is-preparing-chinese-invasion-taiwan-2024-01-31/</link><description>美国越来越担心，未来几年中国国家主席习近平可能会命令军队占领台湾。因此，美国军方正试图在一个关键领域追赶：其后勤网络。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:06:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/logistics-war-how-washington-is-preparing-chinese-invasion-taiwan-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车成立人工智能实验室，与潜在合作伙伴进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/volkswagen-founds-ai-lab-talks-with-potential-partners-2024-01-31/</link><description>大众汽车周三表示，该公司正在与国际科技公司就合作利用人工智能为产品和功能创建新的数字原型进行谈判。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 10:02:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/volkswagen-founds-ai-lab-talks-with-potential-partners-2024-01-31/</guid></item><item><title>香港第四季度GDP同比增长4.3%，慢于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-q4-gdp-expands-43-yy-slower-than-forecast-2024-01-31/</link><description>周三官方预估，香港第四季度经济增速较上年同期加速至 4.3%，入境旅游业和私人消费仍是主要驱动力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 31 Jan 2024 09:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-q4-gdp-expands-43-yy-slower-than-forecast-2024-01-31/</guid></item></channel></rss>